The paper proposes a method for multi-task reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The method involves generating transition dynamics templates, which relates to robotics and control (cs.RO) and system identification (cs.SY). The paper also discusses sample efficiency, which is a common concern in machine learning and optimization (cs.MA).
